<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F57F29 0%, #d66a1f 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      background: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
    }
    .code-box {
      background: white;
      border: 2px solid #F57F29;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }
    .code-value {
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 6px;
      font-family: 'SF Mono', Monaco, 'Courier New', monospace;
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }
    .code-label {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .status-link {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #F57F29;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 32px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 15px;
      margin: 16px 0;
    }
    .status-link:hover {
      background: #d66a1f;
    }
    .info-box {
      background: #e3f2fd;
      border-left: 4px solid #2196f3;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .warning-box {
      background: #fff3cd;
      border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    code {
      background: #f4f4f4;
      padding: 2px 6px;
      border-radius: 3px;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Verify Your Email</h1>
    <p>Start Your Account Migration</p>
    <p>Migration <%= @migration.token %></p>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <p>Hello,</p>

    <p>You've initiated a migration for <strong><%= @migration.old_handle %></strong> to <strong><%= @migration.new_pds_host %></strong>.</p>

    <p>Enter the following verification code on the migration page to start the process:</p>

    <div class="code-box">
      <div class="code-label">Your verification code</div>
      <div class="code-value"><%= @migration.email_verification_token %></div>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="<%= @status_url %>" class="status-link">Go to Migration Page</a>
    </div>

    <div class="info-box">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">What Happens Next?</h3>
      <ul style="margin: 10px 0;">
        <li>Enter the verification code above on the migration page</li>
        <li>Your migration will start automatically</li>
        <li>You'll receive status updates via email</li>
        <li>The entire process takes approximately 20-30 minutes</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="warning-box">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Important Reminders</h3>
      <ul style="margin: 10px 0; margin-bottom: 0;">
        <li><strong>Do not use your account</strong> during the migration</li>
        <li>Any activity during migration will not be transferred</li>
        <li>Close all apps and browser tabs with your account</li>
        <li>Wait for the completion email before logging in again</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Migration Token: <code><%= @migration.token %></code></p>
      <p>If you didn't initiate this migration, please ignore this email.</p>
      <p>Eurosky Migration Service</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
